reviews.text:
This place situated in the middle of forests in Epe, is very nice with an item youHAVE to try; that is a very special pancake, about 3 centimeters high, but very licht and airy, a receipy they own themselves and the pancakes you cannot find anywhere in the world. People come from all over Holland to taste this specialty;
Besides; the staff is very friendly and offer indeed "service with a smile"
Prices of all dishes and drinks affordable, beautiful surroundings!!
